[Captain ng Sawa Agency's
Special Operations Team]

00:40:25.100 --> 00:40:26.690
Sabi mo kanina

00:40:26.690 --> 00:40:27.070
na ang Imperial Army's

00:40:27.070 --> 00:40:27.430
[Huang Gongjie]

