Higit sa lahat,

00:40:35.480 --> 00:40:36.600
ang shareholder dito

00:40:36.600 --> 00:40:38.620
ay ang Deputy Director
ng Economic Bureau ng Macau,

00:40:38.620 --> 00:40:39.390
Ginoong Lok Pak.

00:40:39.390 --> 00:40:41.810
Nasa baba ang kanyang Bachongtian Club.

00:40:41.810 --> 00:40:43.580
Kaya inupahan ko ang buong palapag na ito

00:40:43.580 --> 00:40:45.910
bilang base para sa aming Special Operations Team.

00:40:47.890 --> 00:40:50.460
magaling ka. Napakatalino.

00:40:58.020 --> 00:40:58.600
Lin.

