ay isang charity hospital.

00:42:03.580 --> 00:42:04.730
Sinasaklaw lamang nito ang silid at board,

00:42:04.730 --> 00:42:05.830
walang sweldo.

00:42:06.190 --> 00:42:06.910
Okay.

00:42:08.330 --> 00:42:09.310
Kung mayroong anumang mga titik

00:42:09.310 --> 00:42:10.930
para sa Empresa Comercial Mingshi
sa hinaharap...

00:42:10.930 --> 00:42:11.740
Kaya ko naman sarili ko.

00:42:11.740 --> 00:42:13.050
Mangyaring siguraduhin

00:42:13.350 --> 00:42:14.410
para dalhin sila sa akin.

